%S A393744 1,1,4,21,183,1918,22908,290511,3844666,52453581,733300683,10458157796
%N A393744 Number of free polyominoes in the {8,8} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%F A393744 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q; also P{p,q}(q+1) = P{p,oo}(q+1) + floor((p-1)/2) - floor((3+q(p-2))/2). In this case, p=8, q=8 and P{p,oo} = A389937.
%Y A393744 Cf. A393739, A393740, A393741, A393742, A393743, A389937.
%K A393744 nonn,more,changed
%O A393744 1,3
